{"title":"《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——回溯","uid":"a9b8b88776cf51b021505ec6036cee86","slug":"力扣回溯","date":"2023-12-10T12:03:44.000Z","updated":"2023-12-10T12:18:33.429Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/力扣回溯.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——回溯\"><a href=\"#《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——回溯\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——回溯\"></a>《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——回溯</h1><h2 id=\"1-基础知识\"><a href=\"#1-基础知识\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.基础知识\"></a>1.基础知识</h2><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">find</span><span class=\"params\">(string &amp;s, <span class=\"type\">int</span> i, string &amp;path)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//终止条件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(i == s.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ans.<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(path);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> k=<span class=\"number\">0</span>; k&lt;index[sub].<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); k++)&#123;     <span class=\"comment\">//处理一层</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        path.<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(index[sub][k]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">find</span>(s, i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, path);\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//递归</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        path.<span class=\"built_in\">pop_back</span>();\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//回溯的关键</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//本层的循环处理一层，递归去处理下一层</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"2-标准回溯\"><a href=\"#2-标准回溯\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.标准回溯\"></a>2.标准回溯</h2><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/letter-combinations-of-a-phone-number/description/?envType=study-plan-v2&envId=top-interview-150\">17.电话号码的字母组合</a></p>\n<p>很标注规范的回溯</p>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/combination-sum/description/\">39.组合总和</a></p>\n<p>每个数字都可以重复用，所以每层递归并不一定都会向下走一位，而是原地位进去，sum是返回条件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> index=i; index&lt;<span class=\"number\">9</span>; index++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(sum+nums[index] &lt;= n)\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//剪枝</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"built_in\">find</span>(index, ...);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/combinations/\">77.组合</a></p>\n<p>把第一层函数当做一层展开，就是用for循环，展开一层遍历，用递归去向下延伸</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> index=i; index&lt;nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); index++)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这里的终止条件时path收集到了几位</p>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/subsets/description/\">78.子集</a></p>\n<p>当前位要或者不要，这里就没有for循环了，因为直接就可以分为两种情况进行展开了</p>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/letter-case-permutation/description/\">784.字母大小写全排列</a>  难度分：1342</p>\n<p>分字母和数字进行判断改不改写，怎么递归，常规</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"3-特殊去重\"><a href=\"#3-特殊去重\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.特殊去重\"></a>3.特殊去重</h2><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/combination-sum-ii/description/\">40.组合总和II</a></p>\n<p>终止条件有sum控制，结果集长度不一定相同</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(j-i&gt;<span class=\"number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; nums[j] == nums[j<span class=\"number\">-1</span>])       </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//j-i&gt;0 保证了不会和上一层的重复，而且去重的还是本层的   去重本层，但不去重递归的深层</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">continue</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/combination-sum-iii/\">216.组合总和III</a></p>\n<p>终止条件有sum和len控制</p>\n<p>剪枝+下一位的位数</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> index=i; index&lt;<span class=\"number\">9</span>; index++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(sum+nums[index] &lt;= n)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     path.<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(nums[index]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"built_in\">find</span>(index+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, n, k, path, len+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, sum+nums[index]);\t<span class=\"comment\">//递归进入当前遍历位的下一位</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     path.<span class=\"built_in\">pop_back</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\"> &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/combination-sum-iv/description/\">377.组合总和IV</a></p>\n<p><strong>回溯法翻车了！！！！</strong></p>\n<p>优秀评论：转为爬楼梯的问题，每次爬的层数是从nums里面选出来的，太秀了</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>; i&lt;=target; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">auto</span> num:nums)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(i &gt;= num)</span><br><span class=\"line\">         dp[i] += (<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>)dp[i-num];</span><br><span class=\"line\"> &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/permutations/description/?envType=study-plan-v2&envId=top-interview-150\">46.全排列</a></p>\n<p>不重复数组，借助辅助数组来表示是否加入到path中，回溯即可</p>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/permutations-ii/description/\">47.全排列II</a>  </p>\n<p>全排列，从没选过的里面选一个，结果集长度一定一样，所以终止条件用len判断，去重用bool来判断</p>\n<p>回溯时的剪枝很优秀，相比如让每个元素都来i位，更好理解</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 1 1 2 现在需要剪枝同一层的第二个1收集的答案</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//当第一个1没有被使用的时候，遍历到第二个1，一定要去重</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//如果第一个1现在已经被使用了，那么就可以不再去重，第二个1可以继续使用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(flag[i] == <span class=\"literal\">false</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(i&gt;<span class=\"number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; nums[i]==nums[i<span class=\"number\">-1</span>] &amp;&amp; flag[i<span class=\"number\">-1</span>] == <span class=\"number\">0</span>)    <span class=\"comment\">//这样可以避免子层的剪枝</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/subsets-ii/description/\">90.子集II</a>  </p>\n<p>这个题值得特殊对待，<strong>挑选构成组合问题，不是排列</strong>并且没有sum来当做终止条件</p>\n<p>因为没有终止条件，每次进入递归都会保存，所以不要把他想象成第i位取不取，而是看做一个集合，从集合里面取不取这个数字加入到结果集合中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">find</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt;&amp;nums, <span class=\"type\">int</span> i, vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt;&amp;path)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ans.<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(path);        <span class=\"comment\">//这里相当于不要i位，直接先保存</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> k=i; k&lt;nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); k++)&#123;\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//这里就是带挑选的集合</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(k&gt;i &amp;&amp; nums[k]==nums[k<span class=\"number\">-1</span>])       </span><br><span class=\"line\">         <span class=\"keyword\">continue</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     path.<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(nums[k]);            <span class=\"comment\">//这里为要k位，</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"built_in\">find</span>(nums, k+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, path);</span><br><span class=\"line\">     path.<span class=\"built_in\">pop_back</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\"> &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/generate-parentheses/description/?envType=study-plan-v2&envId=top-interview-150\">22.括号生成</a></p>\n<p>根据左右括号的数量，去确定是否参与递归，这题自己思路完美！！</p>\n<p>那评论区都在噶什么，那么多动态规划</p>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/word-search/description/?envType=study-plan-v2&envId=top-interview-150\">79.单词搜索</a></p>\n<p>一种是在入口之前进行去重，不匹配就不让进行递归，这种代码比较繁琐，而且应该始终都会多递归一层</p>\n<p>还有一种思路是在递归刚进来，处理各种异常return   这种代码简短</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-特例\"><a href=\"#4-特例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.特例\"></a>4.特例</h2><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/permutation-sequence/description/\">60.排列序列</a></p>\n<p>数学方法更优秀，通过确定首位数字后面一个有多少种可能，来确定首位的数字，以此类推</p>\n</blockquote>\n","text":"《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——回溯1.基础知识1234567891011121314void find(string &amp;s, int i, strin...","permalink":"/post/力扣回溯","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.5k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/categories/LeetCode.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/tags/LeetCode.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E3%80%8A%E5%8A%9B%E6%89%A3%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%95150%E9%A2%98%E3%80%8B%E9%A2%98%E5%8D%95%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%9B%9E%E6%BA%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——回溯</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.基础知识</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%9B%9E%E6%BA%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.标准回溯</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E5%8E%BB%E9%87%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.特殊去重</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E7%89%B9%E4%BE%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4.特例</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CYLIN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312241427715.jpg","link":"/","description":"多读书多看报，少吃零食多睡觉","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——双指针","uid":"5b133869c321e07b89f988d13857b0f6","slug":"力扣双指针","date":"2023-12-10T12:03:51.000Z","updated":"2023-12-10T12:20:31.637Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/力扣双指针.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——双指针1.基础知识 为什么双指针会正确？不会漏掉搜索空间 数组nums递增排序，假设共8个元素 假设由于搜索空间i &lt; j...","permalink":"/post/力扣双指针","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/categories/LeetCode.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/tags/LeetCode.json"}],"author":{"name":"CYLIN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312241427715.jpg","link":"/","description":"多读书多看报，少吃零食多睡觉","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——滑动窗口","uid":"653a563cd8843e1e667b0cd176929948","slug":"力扣滑动窗口","date":"2023-12-10T12:03:36.000Z","updated":"2023-12-10T12:18:33.432Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/力扣滑动窗口.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"《力扣面试150题》题单拓展——滑动窗口1.基础知识 先区分好，枚举右端点，还是左端点， 窗口内的条件改变后，一般都是while控制另一个窗口的移动，然后收集结...","permalink":"/post/力扣滑动窗口","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/categories/LeetCode.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/tags/LeetCode.json"}],"author":{"name":"CYLIN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312241427715.jpg","link":"/","description":"多读书多看报，少吃零食多睡觉","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}